unittitle_ssm: Praeger Department of Parks survey and photographs
abstract_ssm: The Praeger Department of Parks survey and photographs document every park, playground, and gore in New York City at the time of the study, as well as undeveloped land owned by the parks department. The survey and photographs show the parks of New York City on the eve of improvements and development funded by the Works Progress Administration.
